sentences: DJ Miki Love (Mihaela Ifrim, born 1984) is a Romanian DJ and dancer, best known for performing in topless in her sets.
She started perforimg in February 2007, in one of the most important clubs Anyin Bucharest, Club Princess, becoming the first topless DJ in Romania.
Love said she had no difficulty performing topless, because she had previously worked as a dancer.
In November 2009 she released her first single, “Black Pussy”, a release that got positive reviews from fans and from Romanian media.
